ce/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"her own path\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"professional soccer\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"medicine\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"her lifelong dream\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"a cardiologist\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"*This interview has been edited for length and clarity.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This interview\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"length\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This conversation took place in November 2023.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This conversation\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How old were you when you first fell in love with soccer and what was it that drew you to the sport?\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michelle Alozie:I definitely got into the sport because my family is Nigerian.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9363757531781788, \"rank\": 0.06193536670972531, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think soccer, or football as they would say, is everything to them.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the youngest of four and all my siblings played soccer so I just blindly went into it just because it was what they were doing and I just had to copy them because I am the baby.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all my siblings\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"the baby\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not think it was until I was around 10, when I actually loved the sport itself instead of doing it because my siblings did it.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"my siblings\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's when I started to take it a little bit more seriously and wanted to see how far things could take me.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you ever imagine that you would be doing this professionally?\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:At the time, I think the professional women's leagues in America just kept folding so I wasn't necessarily sure if there was going to be a professional league or if I would have to go overseas to play football.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the professional women's leagues\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional league\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I continued to grow, the league here also continued to grow and be a little bit more established.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the league\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't until around college that I realized I could play professionally here in the States.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"the States\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SAN JOSE, CALIFORNIA - MARCH 30: Michelle Alozie #11 of the Houston Dash dribbles the ball during a game between Houston Dash and Bay FC at PayPal Park on March 30, 2024 in San Jose, CA.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2304, \"end\": 2312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\", \"score\": 0.9988517228402123, \"rank\": 0.0011495964624871624, \"text\": \"SAN JOSE\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\"}, {\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.6122885031883089, \"rank\": 0.6126494602521084, \"text\": \"CALIFORNIA\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}, {\"begin\": 2337, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.8643938112791438, \"rank\": 0.15644217904632407, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Houston Dash\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\"}, {\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Houston Dash\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\"}, {\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\", \"score\": 0.9988517228402123, \"rank\": 0.0011495964624871624, \"text\": \"San Jose\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"a game\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"Bay FC\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"PayPal Park\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"CA\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Lyndsay Radnedge/ISI Photos/Getty Images) Getty Images There is a quote that says \\\"If opportunity does not knock, create your own door,\\\" and you have done that.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyndsay Radnedge/ISI Photos/Getty Images\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"a quote\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunity\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"your own door\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know it wasn't a straight path to the professional stage for you, you had a couple of doors closed in your face before you got there, but ultimately a few e-mails on your end led to tryouts.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a straight path\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"the professional stage\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2722}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"doors\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"your face\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"ultimately a few e\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"mails\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"your end\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"tryouts\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you talk about how your opportunities with the Houston Dash and the Nigerian national team came about?\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2929, \"end\": 2951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6778123095155805, \"rank\": 0.37486584585457783, \"text\": \"Nigerian national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your opportunities\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the Houston Dash\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:I give her so much credit for this, but I reached out to my old club teammate that I have known since I was maybe 13.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much credit\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"my old club teammate\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was in Houston and told me to email some of the head coaches in the [NWSL], particularly the one in Houston.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9120481163827607, \"rank\": 0.07365580741312502, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 3163, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999783995, \"rank\": 2.162816958008852e-11, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}, {\"begin\": 3194, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9120481163827607, \"rank\": 0.07365580741312502, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She gave me the emails for them and the assistant coaches.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emails\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"the assistant coaches\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I sent them an email just asking for an opportunity.\", \"from\": 326