\"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 4165, \"to\": 4178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:Man playing in the World Cup was surreal, honestly!\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4222}, {\"ngram\": \"Man\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4226}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think even leading up to it once the roster came out, like a month or so before we went out to Australia, it still just did not hit me.\", \"from\": 4275, \"to\": 4412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4372, \"end\": 4381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.819527364385737, \"rank\": 0.18424175402801332, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the roster\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"a month\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember so many people asking me how I felt or what I was feeling and I think it was just like a shock factor.\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many people\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4438}, {\"ngram\": \"a shock factor\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Cup is something I have been watching since I was a kid-both the women's and the men's [tournaments].\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The World Cup\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4554}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4593}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 4599, \"to\": 4608}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4622}, {\"ngram\": \"[tournaments\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So actually having an opportunity to be there just did not seem real, especially since I could not get on a soccer team two years prior.\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"a soccer team\", \"from\": 4746, \"to\": 4759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So now to be at the World Cup with one of the best African teams in Africa I was like 'What is going on?'\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"the best African teams\", \"from\": 4819, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It just did not really hit me!\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 4913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am just so proud of the group that we went with.\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 4950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that a lot of people counted us out, especially being in the \\\"Group of Death\\\".\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 5056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 4998}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5009}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Group\", \"from\": 5035, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"Death\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we also grew a really big fan base from people who were not Nigerian, after beating Australia, tying with Canada and Ireland, and putting up such a good show versus England.\", \"from\": 5057, \"to\": 5238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5149, \"end\": 5158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9850577170822272, \"rank\": 0.01122970507355373