[play] for the U.S. or I am only on Nigeria's [team] because I did not make it on the U.S. team.\", \"from\": 9943, \"to\": 10104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10044, \"end\": 10051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9149259503116611, \"rank\": 0.08802395215435992, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 9951, \"to\": 9956}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9960, \"to\": 9966}, {\"ngram\": \"that misconception\", \"from\": 9972, \"to\": 9990}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 10019, \"to\": 10027}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. team\", \"from\": 10090, \"to\": 10103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But [playing] for the U.S. was never the end goal for me.\", \"from\": 10105, \"to\": 10162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 10123, \"to\": 10131}, {\"ngram\": \"the end goal\", \"from\": 10142, \"to\": 10154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was always to represent being from Nigeria, make my parents and my family back in Nigeria proud, and allow them to live vicariously through me and through this dream that we all had.\", \"from\": 10163, \"to\": 10348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10201, \"end\": 10208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9486412151231371, \"rank\": 0.04072484081390717, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 10248, \"end\": 10255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9486412151231371, \"rank\": 0.04072484081390717, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 10215, \"to\": 10225}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 10230, \"to\": 10239}, {\"ngram\": \"this dream\", \"from\": 10321, \"to\": 10331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michelle's Instagram How much pride do you have in getting to represent Nigeria?\", \"from\": 10350, \"to\": 10431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10350, \"end\": 10358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\", \"score\": 0.8807162119681092, \"rank\": 0.0970484410723028, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\"}, {\"begin\": 10423, \"end\": 10430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9486412151231371, \"rank\": 0.04072484081390717, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"How much pride\", \"from\": 10371, \"to\": 10385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What does that mean to you?\", \"from\": 10432, \"to\": 10459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:It is literally everything!\", \"from\": 10461, \"to\": 10495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 10484, \"to\": 10494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not hit me until I got my call-up in 2021.\", \"from\": 10496, \"to\": 10545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my call-up\", \"from\": 10526, \"to\": 10536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember calling my parents and letting them know, and they were just so shocked and having all my uncles and aunts call me.\", \"from\": 10546, \"to\": 10672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 10565, \"to\": 10575}, {\"ngram\": \"all my uncles\", \"from\": 10640, \"to\": 10653}, {\"ngram\": \"aunts\", \"from\": 10658, \"to\": 10663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just so surreal and it made me so happy that even though I was born in America and I only had been to Nigeria once in my life before that, I would want to represent the family and our culture and show just the pride that I have in being Nigerian.\", \"from\": 10673, \"to\": 10926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10782, \"end\": 10789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9486412151231371, \"rank\": 0.04072484081390717, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 10751, \"to\": 10758}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 10798, \"to\": 10805}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 10845, \"to\": 10855}, {\"ngram\": \"our culture\", \"from\": 10860, \"to\": 10871}, {\"ngram\": \"just the pride\", \"from\": 10881, \"to\": 10895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigerian pride is strong, that's for sure and I think I have definitely grown into that pride as I have gotten older.\", \"from\": 10927, \"to\": 11044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10927, \"end\": 10935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.7054425998554474, \"rank\": 0.39554163980670165, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that pride\", \"from\": 11010, \"to\": 11020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do you think it means to your parents that you get to represent Nigeria?\", \"from\": 11046, \"to\": 11123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11115, \"end\": 11122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.5797332054300913, \"rank\": 0.5998689683005659, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your parents\", \"from\": 11076, \"to\": 11088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:They love it!\", \"from\": 11125, \"to\": 11145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think they are all just so confused at how this little one who was just following her siblings' footsteps, made it to the Nigerian team.\", \"from\": 11146, \"to\": 11284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11270, \"end\": 11278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.5478954498946087, \"rank\": 0.7209242418041565, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this little one\", \"from\": 11191, \"to\": 11206}, {\"ngram\": \"her siblings' footsteps\", \"from\": 11230, \"to\": 11253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are just so happy.\", \"from\": 11285, \"to\": 11308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They always take credit.\", \"from\": 11309, \"to\": 11333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"credit\", \"from\": 11326, \"to\": 11332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are like, 'Oh, remember when we were doing those shooting drills in San Diego in your backyard?\", \"from\": 11334, \"to\": 11434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11411, \"end\": 11416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.9806593648262523, \"rank\": 0.019718946111299325, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those shooting drills\", \"from\": 11382, \"to\": 11403}, {\"ngram\": \"your backyard\", \"from\": 11420, \"to\": 11433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the reason you are [playing for] Nigeria.\", \"from\": 11435, \"to\": 11483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 11442, \"to\": 11452}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigeria\", \"from\": 11475, \"to\": 11482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am like, yeah that actually is the reason.\", \"from\": 11484, \"to\": 11528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 11517, \"to\": 11527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So any opportunity I have to just make them proud and allow them to come to one of our games just makes me so happy and I feel like it really fulfills the family.\", \"from\": 11529, \"to\": 11691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any opportunity\", \"from\": 11532, \"to\": 11547}, {\"ngram\": \"our games\", \"from\": 11612, \"to\": 11621}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 11680, \"to\": 11690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BRISBANE, AUSTRALIA - JULY 16: Michelle Alozie of Nigeria poses for a portrait during the official FIFA Women's World Cup Australia & New Zealand 2023 portrait session on July 16, 2023 in Brisbane, Australia.\", \"from\": 11693, \"to\": 11901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11724, \"end\": 11732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"score\": 0.6025048350385864, \"rank\": 0.6531440578519012, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\"}, {\"begin\": 11792, \"end\": 11796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9720353248445487, \"rank\": 0.02868327452675589, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 11805, \"end\": 11814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9422992512271354, \"rank\": 0.03979947638243039, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 11815, \"end\": 11824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_so