\"from\": 11902, \"to\": 12052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11912, \"end\": 11922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"score\": 0.9999752325781989, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hyde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hyde\"}, {\"begin\": 11925, \"end\": 11929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9720353248445487, \"rank\": 0.02868327452675589, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 11939, \"end\": 11944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.99967526274705, \"rank\": 0.000119173681787516, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 11963, \"end\": 11968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.99967526274705, \"rank\": 0.000119173681787516, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 11979, \"to\": 11985}, {\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 12004, \"to\": 12013}, {\"ngram\": \"sacrifices\", \"from\": 12017, \"to\": 12027}, {\"ngram\": \"your parents\", \"from\": 12032, \"to\": 12044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What are some hardships that Nigerian immigrants that people do not necessarily see?\", \"from\": 12053, \"to\": 12137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12082, \"end\": 12090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.7568716942869185, \"rank\": 0.3196280401934118, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some hardships\", \"from\": 12062, \"to\": 12076}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 12107, \"to\": 12113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:My parents came [to the U.S.] in their mid-20s to come to college.\", \"from\": 12139, \"to\": 12212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 12139, \"to\": 12145}, {\"ngram\": \"My parents\", \"from\": 12146, \"to\": 12156}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 12166, \"to\": 12174}, {\"ngram\": \"their mid-20s\", \"from\": 12179, \"to\": 12192}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 12204, \"to\": 12211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At first, my mom was in Canada, my dad was in Texas.\", \"from\": 12213, \"to\": 12265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12237, \"end\": 12243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.5427319260528698, \"rank\": 0.6978657760832012, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 12259, \"end\": 12264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9869041912997732, \"rank\": 0.008924635333424476, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mom\", \"from\": 12223, \"to\": 12229}, {\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 12245, \"to\": 12251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their whole focus-which I think we also forget when we are younger-was to bring their family to America as well because they were the first to come to America on both sides.\", \"from\": 12266, \"to\": 12439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their whole focus\", \"from\": 12266, \"to\": 12283}, {\"ngram\": \"their family\", \"from\": 12346, \"to\": 12358}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 12362, \"to\": 12369}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 12417, \"to\": 12424}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 12428, \"to\": 12438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were focused on making it successfully, [earning] money, and either sending it back home or [providing] for their family to come.\", \"from\": 12440, \"to\": 12574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 12495, \"to\": 12500}, {\"ngram\": \"their family\", \"from\": 12553, \"to\": 12565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As they were doing that, they were also just trying to figure out their life, make life for us as amazing as they could, and provide different opportunities that they did not have in Nigeria, or they fought really hard to then come to America for.\", \"from\": 12575, \"to\": 12822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12758, \"end\": 12765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9979318416203182, \"rank\": 0.0015871197021257346, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their life\", \"from\": 12641, \"to\": 12651}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 12658, \"to\": 12662}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 12667, \"to\": 12669}, {\"ngram\": \"different opportunities\", \"from\": 12708, \"to\": 12731}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 12810, \"to\": 12817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were not allowed to make the mistakes that I am allowed to make right now, or when I was 25 or 26, they had to be almost completely perfect.\", \"from\": 12824, \"to\": 12969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mistakes\", \"from\": 12854, \"to\": 12866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were not allowed to be like, 'I will just play soccer right now.\", \"from\": 12970, \"to\": 13039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 13022, \"to\": 13028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will figure out my life later and maybe go to med school later.'\", \"from\": 13040, \"to\": 13106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 13058, \"to\": 13065}, {\"ngram\": \"med school\", \"from\": 13088, \"to\": 13098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had to have a really strict plan because it wasn't just them that they were worried about.\", \"from\": 13107, \"to\": 13202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really strict plan\", \"from\": 13124, \"to\": 13144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were trying to make life better for their whole entire family.\", \"from\": 13203, \"to\": 13270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 13228, \"to\": 13232}, {\"ngram\": \"their whole entire family\", \"from\": 13244, \"to\": 13269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's just amazing because being [in my 20s] right now, I still feel like I am a kid, and for them to have moved to a different country trying to make life for their entire family better and bring them to America-I just can not imagine doing that at my age.\", \"from\": 13272, \"to\": 13536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my 20s\", \"from\": 13316, \"to\": 13322}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 13358, \"to\": 13363}, {\"ngram\": \"a different country\", \"from\": 13395, \"to\": 13414}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 13430, \"to\": 13434}, {\"ngram\": \"their entire family\", \"from\": 13439, \"to\": 13458}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 13484, \"to\": 13491}, {\"ngram\": \"my age\", \"from\": 13529, \"to\": 13535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a really nice way of putting that.\", \"from\": 13538, \"to\": 13579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really nice way\", \"from\": 13545, \"to\": 13562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for sharing that!\", \"from\": 13580, \"to\": 13607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What are some things that only people who grew up in an African household would understand?\", \"from\": 13608, \"to\": 13699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some things\", \"from\": 13617, \"to\": 13628}, {\"ngram\": \"only people\", \"from\": 13634, \"to\": 13645}, {\"ngram\": \"an African household\", \"from\": 13661, \"to\": 13681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:Hmmm.. when family comes over and all you want to do is go to your room and you walk in and find like 14 kids just sleeping on you are bed and you are just like 'Who are you guys?'\", \"from\": 13701, \"to\": 13888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 13701, \"to\": 13707}, {\"ngram\": \"Hmmm\", \"from\": 13708, \"to\": 13712}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 13720, \"to\": 13726}, {\"ngram\": \"your room\", \"from\": 13770, \"to\": 13779}, {\"ngram\": \"14 kids\", \"from\": 13810, \"to\": 13817}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 13843, \"to\": 13846}, {\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 13878, \"to\": 13886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are your cousins and you are just like 'Alright, whatever I guess I just will not be in my room today.'\", \"from\": 13889, \"to\": 13997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your cousins\", \"from\": 13898, \"to\": 13910}, {\"ngram\": \"Alright\", \"from\": 13934, \"to\": 13941}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 13943, \"to\": 13951}, {\"ngram\": \"my room\", \"from\": 13982, \"to\": 13989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is hilarious!\", \"from\": 13999, \"to\": 14017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What are some values from your culture that have turned you into the person you are today?Alozie:The worth ethic.\", \"from\": 14018, \"to\": 14131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some values\", \"from\": 14027, \"to\": 14038}, {\"ngram\": \"your culture\", \"from\": 14044, \"to\": 14056}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 14083, \"to\": 14093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a really good stereotype that Nigerians have.\", \"from\": 14132, \"to\": 14184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good stereotype\", \"from\": 14139, \"to\": 14163}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigerians\", \"from\": 14169, \"to\": 14178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will work tirelessly and endlessly to get what they want.\", \"from\": 14185, \"to\": 14247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that I have done that throughout my scholastic career and also now in my professional career.\", \"from\": 14248, \"to\": 14349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my scholastic career\", \"from\": 14289, \"to\": 14309}, {\"ngram\": \"my professional career\", \"from\": 14326, \"to\": 14348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will put work into everything just to make sure that things come to fruition the way I see them.\", \"from\": 14350, \"to\": 14448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 14361, \"to\": 14365}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 14371, \"to\": 14381}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 14405, \"to\": 14411}, {\"ngram\": \"fruition\", \"from\": 14420, \"to\": 14428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of my not sleeping or having to miss out on things.\", \"from\": 14449, \"to\": 14511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 14504, \"to\": 14510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will do what I have to do to make sure that something works out the way that I [envision] it.\", \"from\": 14512, \"to\": 14607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 14558, \"to\": 14567}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 14578, \"to\": 14585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BRISBANE, AUSTRALIA - AUGUST 7: Michelle Alozie of Nigeria and Keira Walsh of England battle for the ball during the FIFA Women's World Cup Australia & New Zealand 2023 Round of 16 match between England and Nigeria at Brisbane Stadium on August 7, 2023 in Brisbane, Australia.\", \"from\": 14609, \"to\": 14885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14641, \"end\": 14649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc