ies\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 15055, \"to\": 15061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:It means regardless of what we are doing or what situation we are in, we will not be trampled.\", \"from\": 15109, \"to\": 15210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what situation\", \"from\": 15160, \"to\": 15174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will never catch us slipping.\", \"from\": 15211, \"to\": 15244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 15232, \"to\": 15234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigeria will always come prideful.\", \"from\": 15245, \"to\": 15279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nigeria\", \"from\": 15245, \"to\": 15252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will come right.\", \"from\": 15280, \"to\": 15299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will come with receipts.\", \"from\": 15300, \"to\": 15327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"receipts\", \"from\": 15318, \"to\": 15326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will come with everything, prepared to be the best.\", \"from\": 15328, \"to\": 15382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 15346, \"to\": 15356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We always think we are the best which also helps but [Nigerians] will always come on top at the end of whatever situation that we are in.\", \"from\": 15383, \"to\": 15520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nigerians\", \"from\": 15437, \"to\": 15446}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 15468, \"to\": 15471}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 15475, \"to\": 15482}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever situation\", \"from\": 15486, \"to\": 15504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have heard you talk about the fight of the Nigerian national team.\", \"from\": 15522, \"to\": 15590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15567, \"end\": 15589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5243766972899716, \"rank\": 0.7939418549561498, \"text\": \"Nigerian national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 15550, \"to\": 15559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How does that saying and mentality spill over into the Super Falcon's work ethic?\", \"from\": 15591, \"to\": 15672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mentality spill\", \"from\": 15616, \"to\": 15631}, {\"ngram\": \"the Super Falcon's work ethic\", \"from\": 15642, \"to\": 15671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:I am only going into my third season with the Nigerian team and just to hear what they have put themselves through from such a young age-some people have been on the team for 20 years plus and they have been able to triumph and work for so much.\", \"from\": 15674, \"to\": 15926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15727, \"end\": 15735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.8179111149029058, \"rank\": 0.22021549492150283, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 15674, \"to\": 15680}, {\"ngram\": \"my third season\", \"from\": 15702, \"to\": 15717}, {\"ngram\": \"such a young age\", \"from\": 15801, \"to\": 15817}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 15818, \"to\": 15829}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 15843, \"to\": 15851}, {\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 15856, \"to\": 15864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think a lot of people do not see things that happen behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 15928, \"to\": 16000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 15936, \"to\": 15941}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 15945, \"to\": 15951}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 15963, \"to\": 15969}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 15989, \"to\": 15999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Super Falcons, it's way more than just performing on the field, we have to do so much behind the scenes that people do not really know and we can not really talk about.\", \"from\": 16001, \"to\": 16178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16010, \"end\": 16023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 16063, \"to\": 16072}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 16103, \"to\": 16113}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 16119, \"to\": 16125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Football always brings so much pride and happiness to Nigerians and so I think for them to put everything aside and still be able to perform their hearts out-blood, sweat, and tears-just to make others happy shows our work ethic.\", \"from\": 16179, \"to\": 16408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Football\", \"from\": 16179, \"to\": 16187}, {\"ngram\": \"so much pride\", \"from\": 16202, \"to\": 16215}, {\"ngram\": \"happiness\", \"from\": 16220, \"to\": 16229}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigerians\", \"from\": 16233, \"to\": 16242}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 16274, \"to\": 16284}, {\"ngram\": \"their hearts\", \"from\": 16320, \"to\": 16332}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 16337, \"to\": 16342}, {\"ngram\": \"sweat\", \"from\": 16344, \"to\": 16349}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 16355, \"to\": 16360}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 16374, \"to\": 16380}, {\"ngram\": \"our work\", \"from\": 16393, \"to\": 16401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigeria players react to a missed shot by Michelle Alozie (not pictured) during a penalty shoot-out after extra time in the FIFA Women's World Cup, Round of 16 match at Brisbane Stadium, Australia.\", \"from\": 16410, \"to\": 16607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16452, \"end\": 16460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"score\": 0.673251746809743, \"rank\": 0.41504164260735854, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\"}, {\"begin\": 16597, \"end\": 16606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9998060094765282, \"rank\": 0.0001923871782996912, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nigeria players\", \"from\": 16410, \"to\": 16425}, {\"ngram\": \"a missed shot\", \"from\": 16435, \"to\": 16448}, {\"ngram\": \"a penalty shoot-out\", \"from\": 16490, \"to\": 16509}, {\"ngram\": \"extra time\", \"from\": 16516, \"to\": 16526}, {\"ngram\": \"the FIFA Women's World Cup\", \"from\": 16530, \"to\": 16556}, {\"ngram\": \"16 match\", \"from\": 16567, \"to\": 16575}, {\"ngram\": \"Brisbane Stadium\", \"from\": 16579, \"to\": 16595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture date: Monday August 7, 2023.\", \"from\": 16608, \"to\": 16644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture date\", \"from\": 16608, \"to\": 16620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Isabel Infantes/PA Images via Getty Images) PA Images via Getty Images What is the overall team dynamic like?\", \"from\": 16645, \"to\": 16766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16685, \"end\": 16690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9994421457820574, \"rank\": 0.0004733140474070085, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 16700, \"end\": 16702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_address_system\", \"score\": 0.9364361561393402, \"rank\": 0.06067714048775551, \"text\": \"PA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_address_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_address_system\"}, {\"begin\": 16714, \"end\": 16719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9994421457820574, \"rank\": 0.0004733140474070085, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 16645, \"to\": 16651}, {\"ngram\": \"Isabel Infantes/PA Images\", \"from\": 16655, \"to\": 16680}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall team\", \"from\": 16734, \"to\": 16750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:Oh, it's so funny!\", \"from\": 16768, \"to\": 16793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 16768, \"to\": 16774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think when I first joined I was so confused.\", \"from\": 16794, \"to\": 16840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of them wanted to call them 'aunties' and I remember thinking 'Whoa, what is this?\", \"from\": 16841, \"to\": 16928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'aunties\", \"from\": 16874, \"to\": 16882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are my teammate.'\", \"from\": 16929, \"to\": 16950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my teammate\", \"from\": 16937, \"to\": 16948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after getting to know them they are all just so kind and friendly, and they genuinely want the best for you and the team.\", \"from\": 16952, \"to\": 17077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 17068, \"to\": 17076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are all willing to quickly sacrifice-especially the ones who have been there the longest-for the younger generation, which I think is beautiful.\", \"from\": 17078, \"to\": 17227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"especially the ones\", \"from\": 17120, \"to\": 17139}, {\"ngram\": \"the longest-for the younger generation\", \"from\": 17160, \"to\": 17198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the only way things can really change.\", \"from\": 17228, \"to\": 17271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only way\", \"from\": 17233, \"to\": 17245}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 17246, \"to\": 17252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's definitely a group of sisters and I am so glad to have been able to meet all of the ones that I have these past three years.\", \"from\": 17272, \"to\": 17401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 17288, \"to\": 17295}, {\"ngram\": \"sisters\", \"from\": 17299, \"to\": 17306}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 17357, \"to\": 17365}, {\"ngram\": \"these past three years\", \"from\": 17378, \"to\": 17400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aww I love that!\", \"from\": 17403, \"to\": 17419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So did you grow up watching the Olympics at all?\", \"from\": 17420, \"to\": 17468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 17448, \"to\": 17460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a favorite Olympic memory?\", \"from\": 17469, \"to\": 17507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a favorite Olympic memory\", \"from\": 17481, \"to\": 17506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:Honestly I did not really watch the Olympics that much growing up.\", \"from\": 17509, \"to\": 17582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 17509, \"to\": 17515}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 17548, \"to\": 17560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really just watched the World Cup.\", \"from\": 17583, \"to\": 17619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 17605, \"to\": 17618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not really watch the Summer Olympics but I do remember watching the Winter Olympics and loving curling for some reason because I just thought that it was so interesting and it looked really tedious.You have had the opportunity to represent Nigeria at the World Cup and get a taste of playing on the world's biggest stage.\", \"from\": 17620, \"to\": 17947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17866, \"end\": 17873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6377476719993603, \"rank\": 0.47841798187094153, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 17643, \"to\": 17662}, {\"ngram\": \"the Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 17690, \"to\": 17709}, {\"ngram\": \"some reason\", \"from\": 17733, \"to\": 17744}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 17837, \"to\": 17852}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 17877, \"to\": 17890}, {\"ngram\": \"a taste\", \"from\": 17899, \"to\": 17906}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest stage\", \"from\": 17921, \"to\": 17946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What would having the opportunity to represent Nigeria at an Olympic Games mean to you?\", \"from\": 17948, \"to\": 18035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17995, \"end\": 18002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6377476719993603, \"rank\": 0.47841798187094153, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 17966, \"to\": 17981}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 18006, \"to\": 18022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:The Olympics would be insane!\", \"from\": 18037, \"to\": 18073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 18037, \"to\": 18043}, {\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 18044, \"to\": 18056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To put it into perspective, the Nigerian team has not made it to the Olympics since 2008.\", \"from\": 18074, \"to\": 18163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18106, \"end\": 18114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.5257966292699386, \"rank\": 0.7364388327998331, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 18089, \"to\": 18100}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 18139, \"to\": 18151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although we have made it to every World Cup, it's the Olympics that seems to hinder us a bit for some reason.\", \"from\": 18164, \"to\": 18273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every World Cup\", \"from\": 18192, \"to\": 18207}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 18214, \"to\": 18226}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 18248, \"to\": 18250}, {\"ngram\": \"some reason\", \"from\": 18261, \"to\": 18272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So to just have the Super Falcons back at the Olympics would be amazing!\", \"from\": 18274, \"to\": 18346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18294, \"end\": 18307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 18316, \"to\": 18328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But also after having such an amazing run in the World Cup, to be able to put on a performance again in the Olympics would be amazing!\", \"from\": 18347, \"to\": 18481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such an amazing run\", \"from\": 18369, \"to\": 18388}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 18392, \"to\": 18405}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance\", \"from\": 18428, \"to\": 18441}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 18451, \"to\": 18463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would just show the gap that is closing between what everyone says is the best soccer-[teams] from Europe or the Americas-and show that African soccer is really closing that gap.\", \"from\": 18482, \"to\": 18663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 18501, \"to\": 18508}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 18538, \"to\": 18546}, {\"ngram\": \"the best soccer-[teams\", \"from\": 18555, \"to\": 18577}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 18584, \"to\": 18590}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americas\", \"from\": 18594, \"to\": 18606}, {\"ngram\": \"African soccer\", \"from\": 18621, \"to\": 18635}, {\"ngram\": \"that gap\", \"from\": 18654, \"to\": 18662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Africa has never hosted an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 18665, \"to\": 18706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 18665, \"to\": 18671}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 18689, \"to\": 18705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you think that will ever happen and what needs to change?\", \"from\": 18707, \"to\": 18767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:Man, I actually did not even realize that the Olympics was never in Africa!\", \"from\": 18769, \"to\": 18851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Man\", \"from\": 18776, \"to\": 18779}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 18818, \"to\": 18830}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 18844, \"to\": 18850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think having the World Cup in South Africa, showed that there is value being in Africa.\", \"from\": 18852, \"to\": 18941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18884, \"end\": 18896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9975814893436159, \"rank\": 0.001662471350313578, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 18867, \"to\": 18880}, {\"ngram\": \"value\", \"from\": 18919, \"to\": 18924}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 18934, \"to\": 18940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is the stereotype that there is nothing in Africa and it's kind of just barren, but in reality, there is so much beauty in Africa!\", \"from\": 18942, \"to\": 19078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stereotype\", \"from\": 18951, \"to\": 18965}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 18980, \"to\": 18987}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 18991, \"to\": 18997}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 19035, \"to\": 19042}, {\"ngram\": \"so much beauty\", \"from\": 19053, \"to\": 19067}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 19071, \"to\": 19077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So many great infrastructures can be built for it to host an Olympics just like they did for the World Cup.\", \"from\": 19079, \"to\": 19186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"So many great infrastructures\", \"from\": 19079, \"to\": 19108}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 19137, \"to\": 19148}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 19172, \"to\": 19185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really hope that there can be an Olympics in Africa in the near future.\", \"from\": 19187, \"to\": 19260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 19219, \"to\": 19230}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 19234, \"to\": 19240}, {\"ngram\": \"the near future\", \"from\": 19244, \"to\": 19259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not see why there should not be one.\", \"from\": 19261, \"to\": 19302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Soccer and Nigerian culture is just one portion of your life.\", \"from\": 19304, \"to\": 19365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19315, \"end\": 19323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.6706568332081397, \"rank\": 0.4885730360017114, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one portion\", \"from\": 19335, \"to\": 19351}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 19355, \"to\": 19364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You got your undergraduate degree from Yale in molecular, cellular, and developmental biology with the dream of becoming a cardiologist.\", \"from\": 19366, \"to\": 19502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19405, \"end\": 19409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yale_University\", \"score\": 0.9999991948403535, \"rank\": 6.131422838464731e-07, \"text\": \"Yale\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yale_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yale_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your undergraduate degree\", \"from\": 19374, \"to\": 19399}, {\"ngram\": \"molecular, cellular, and developmental biology\", \"from\": 19413, \"to\": 19459}, {\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 19465, \"to\": 19474}, {\"ngram\": \"a cardiologist\", \"from\": 19487, \"to\": 19501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did that dream come about?\", \"from\": 19503, \"to\": 19533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that dream\", \"from\": 19511, \"to\": 19521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:From a young age, I was obsessed with animals and I really wanted to be a veterinarian.\", \"from\": 19535, \"to\": 19629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 19547, \"to\": 19558}, {\"ngram\": \"animals\", \"from\": 19580, \"to\": 19587}, {\"ngram\": \"a veterinarian\", \"from\": 19614, \"to\": 19628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember telling my parents that and they were like 'You are not going to be a veterinarian.\", \"from\": 19630, \"to\": 19724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 19649, \"to\": 19659}, {\"ngram\": \"a veterinarian\", \"from\": 19709, \"to\": 19723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to help animals, help humans they are animals too.\", \"from\": 19725, \"to\": 19787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"animals\", \"from\": 19745, \"to\": 19752}, {\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 19759, \"to\": 19765}, {\"ngram\": \"animals\", \"from\": 19775, \"to\": 19782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can be a doctor.'\", \"from\": 19788, \"to\": 19809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a doctor\", \"from\": 19799, \"to\": 19807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I thought 'Oh okay, I can be a doctor.'\", \"from\": 19810, \"to\": 19853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a doctor\", \"from\": 19843, \"to\": 19851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always enjoyed biology.\", \"from\": 19855, \"to\": 19880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"biology\", \"from\": 19872, \"to\": 19879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was always my favorite subject in school so it just seemed like a no-brainer.\", \"from\": 19881, \"to\": 19963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my favorite subject\", \"from\": 19897, \"to\": 19916}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 19920, \"to\": 19926}, {\"ngram\": \"a no-brainer\", \"from\": 19950, \"to\": 19962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of my senior year, I ended up working with a cardiovascular and therapeutics lab for my senior thesis.\", \"from\": 19964, \"to\": 20077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 19967, \"to\": 19974}, {\"ngram\": \"my senior year\", \"from\": 19978, \"to\": 19992}, {\"ngram\": \"a cardiovascular and therapeutics lab\", \"from\": 20018, \"to\": 20055}, {\"ngram\": \"my senior thesis\", \"from\": 20060, \"to\": 20076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In working with the Dardik lab I learned that this was a really fun, niche field and that it wasn't really populated with women or with women of color.\", \"from\": 20078, \"to\": 20229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Dardik lab\", \"from\": 20094, \"to\": 20108}, {\"ngram\": \"a really fun, niche field\", \"from\": 20133, \"to\": 20158}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 20200, \"to\": 20205}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 20214, \"to\": 20219}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 20223, \"to\": 20228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I thought that, that would be an amazing place for me to be in.\", \"from\": 20230, \"to\": 20296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing place\", \"from\": 20263, \"to\": 20279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSTON, TEXAS - SEPTEMBER 7: Texas Childrens Hospital Cancer Research Technician 3 Michelle Alozie laughs while talking to colleagues Wednesday, Aug. 30, 2023 at Texas Children's Cancer and Hematology Center in Houston.\", \"from\": 20298, \"to\": 20518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20298, \"end\": 20312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.999995274138226, \"rank\": 4.1215693146852775e-06, \"text\": \"HOUSTON, TEXAS\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 20328, \"end\": 20333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9953955862521925, \"rank\": 0.004593728960736816, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 20334, \"end\": 20352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Childrens_Hospital\", \"score\": 0.9999999989776143, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Childrens Hospital\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Childrens_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Childrens_Hospital\"}, {\"begin\": 20461, \"end\": 20466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9953955862521925, \"rank\": 0.004593728960736816, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 20489, \"end\": 20499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hematology\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hematology\", \"types\": [\"Q930752\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hematology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hematology\"}, {\"begin\": 20510, \"end\": 20517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9998129973709853, \"rank\": 0.00018531627338427134, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"- SEPTEMBER\", \"from\": 20313, \"to\": 20324}, {\"ngram\": \"Technician\", \"from\": 20369, \"to\": 20379}, {\"ngram\": \"colleagues\", \"from\": 20422, \"to\": 20432}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 20444, \"to\": 20448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Yi-Chin Lee/Houston Chronicle via Getty Images) Houston Chronicle via Getty Images I read that when you were younger you wanted your parents to bring you back a goat heart from the market.\", \"from\": 20519, \"to\": 20710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20528, \"end\": 20531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9240546738531384, \"rank\": 0.04323214744977935, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 20554, \"end\": 20559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Paul_Getty_III\", \"score\": 0.9868610873623788, \"rank\": 0.006264939863114851, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Paul_Getty_III\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Paul_Getty_III\"}, {\"begin\": 20569, \"end\": 20586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Chronicle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Houston Chronicle\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Chronicle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Chronicle\"}, {\"begin\": 20591, \"end\": 20596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Paul_Getty_III\", \"score\": 0.9868610873623788, \"rank\": 0.006264939863114851, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Paul_Getty_III\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Paul_Getty_III\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your parents\", \"from\": 20648, \"to\": 20660}, {\"ngram\": \"a goat heart\", \"from\": 20679, \"to\": 20691}, {\"ngram\": \"the market\", \"from\": 20697, \"to\": 20707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did that actually ever happen?\", \"from\": 20711, \"to\": 20741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:No they did not!\", \"from\": 20743, \"to\": 20766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 20743, \"to\": 20749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was so obsessed because I think pig and goat hearts are actually very similar to human hearts.\", \"from\": 20767, \"to\": 20863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pig\", \"from\": 20801, \"to\": 20804}, {\"ngram\": \"goat hearts\", \"from\": 20809, \"to\": 20820}, {\"ngram\": \"human hearts\", \"from\": 20850, \"to\": 20862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought that's the closest thing I'd have to a human heart which would be so cool!\", \"from\": 20864, \"to\": 20948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closest thing\", \"from\": 20881, \"to\": 20898}, {\"ngram\": \"a human heart\", \"from\": 20911, \"to\": 20924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like if they just put it in formaldehyde, I can preserve it, and I can have it on my bed.\", \"from\": 20949, \"to\": 21044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"formaldehyde\", \"from\": 20983, \"to\": 20995}, {\"ngram\": \"my bed\", \"from\": 21037, \"to\": 21043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They probably thought I was the weirdest child ever.\", \"from\": 21045, \"to\": 21097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weirdest child\", \"from\": 21073, \"to\": 21091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I just thought that'd be so cool to have a heart because they were going to a slaughterhouse anyway.\", \"from\": 21098, \"to\": 21202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a heart\", \"from\": 21143, \"to\": 21150}, {\"ngram\": \"a slaughterhouse\", \"from\": 21178, \"to\": 21194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that never happened but it was probably for the better.\", \"from\": 21203, \"to\": 21261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When you are not playing soccer you work as a cancer research technician at Texas Children's Cancer and Hematology Center.\", \"from\": 21263, \"to\": 21385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21339, \"end\": 21344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9919907048131922, \"rank\": 0.007930681617845207, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 21367, \"end\": 21377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hematology\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hematology\", \"types\": [\"Q930752\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hematology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hematology\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 21288, \"to\": 21294}, {\"ngram\": \"a cancer research technician\", \"from\": 21307, \"to\": 21335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you explain what you do there?\", \"from\": 21386, \"to\": 21420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:Yeah, so in my lab withDr.\", \"from\": 21422, \"to\": 21455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 21422, \"to\": 21428}, {\"ngram\": \"my lab withDr\", \"from\": 21441, \"to\": 21454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Stevens, alongsideDr.\", \"from\": 21456, \"to\": 21487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21456, \"end\": 21465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Alexandra_of_Greece_and_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.8006922756106257, \"rank\": 0.24530463900838967, \"text\": \"Alexandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Alexandra_of_Greece_and_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Alexandra_of_Greece_and_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"alongsideDr\", \"from\": 21475, \"to\": 21486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adel, we work on chemotherapies and see how these different cancers are able to resist these chemotherapies.\", \"from\": 21488, \"to\": 21596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chemotherapies\", \"from\": 21505, \"to\": 21519}, {\"ngram\": \"these different cancers\", \"from\": 21532, \"to\": 21555}, {\"ngram\": \"these chemotherapies\", \"from\": 21575, \"to\": 21595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We try to figure out the best ways to give these chemotherapies in conjunction with another or just by themselves, and how they will be able to eradicate these patients' cancers.\", \"from\": 21597, \"to\": 21775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best ways\", \"from\": 21618, \"to\": 21631}, {\"ngram\": \"the