rce/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.898130115519906, \"rank\": 0.07393868884086675, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 22268, \"end\": 22285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Chronicle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Houston Chronicle\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Chronicle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Chronicle\"}, {\"begin\": 22290, \"end\": 22295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.898130115519906, \"rank\": 0.07393868884086675, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing work\", \"from\": 22310, \"to\": 22322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you still plan on going to medical school after your soccer career to be a cardiologist?\", \"from\": 22345, \"to\": 22436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medical school\", \"from\": 22375, \"to\": 22389}, {\"ngram\": \"your soccer career\", \"from\": 22396, \"to\": 22414}, {\"ngram\": \"a cardiologist\", \"from\": 22421, \"to\": 22435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:I still have that passion for sure!\", \"from\": 22438, \"to\": 22480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alozie\", \"from\": 22438, \"to\": 22444}, {\"ngram\": \"that passion\", \"from\": 22458, \"to\": 22470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think being out of school for this long, does make it a little weary, I will be honest.\", \"from\": 22481, \"to\": 22570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 22502, \"to\": 22508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able to work with Dr. Stevens and Dr. Adel, and seeing the interactions they have with their patients, and just how much they care for them is something that I yearn for and I still really want to do, obviously, in a different field.\", \"from\": 22571, \"to\": 22810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22615, \"end\": 22619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VIII\", \"score\": 0.9999530472448517, \"rank\": 4.695453638717209e-05, \"text\": \"Adel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VIII\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VIII\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dr. Stevens\", \"from\": 22595, \"to\": 22606}, {\"ngram\": \"the interactions\", \"from\": 22632, \"to\": 22648}, {\"ngram\": \"their patients\", \"from\": 22664, \"to\": 22678}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 22720, \"to\": 22729}, {\"ngram\": \"a different field\", \"from\": 22792, \"to\": 22809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think the dream remains the same.\", \"from\": 22811, \"to\": 22850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 22823, \"to\": 22832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be 30-something in med school but that's just what it will have to take.\", \"from\": 22851, \"to\": 22930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30-something\", \"from\": 22861, \"to\": 22873}, {\"ngram\": \"med school\", \"from\": 22877, \"to\": 22887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hey, it's never too late!\", \"from\": 22932, \"to\": 22957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know everyone always asks you how you balance it all but I truly believe that if you love something enough, you will make it work so my question for you is what keeps you going?\", \"from\": 22958, \"to\": 23137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 22965, \"to\": 22973}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 23050, \"to\": 23059}, {\"ngram\": \"my question\", \"from\": 23093, \"to\": 23104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alozie:I think it's just the genuine love that I have for doing both things.\", \"from\": 23139, \"to\": 23215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the genuine love\", \"from\": 23164, \"to\": 23180}, {\"ngram\": \"both things\", \"from\": 23203, \"to\": 23214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Football has been just a childhood love of mine.\", \"from\": 23216, \"to\": 23264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Football\", \"from\": 23216, \"to\": 23224}, {\"ngram\": \"just a childhood love\", \"from\": 23234, \"to\": 23255}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 23259, \"to\": 23263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just can never give up that dream or stop myself early from doing that and fulfilling that.\", \"from\": 23265, \"to\": 23358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that dream\", \"from\": 23290, \"to\": 23300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The medical field has been a dream of mine that's continuing to grow... it's like my adult dream.\", \"from\": 23359, \"to\": 23456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The medical field\", \"from\": 23359, \"to\": 23376}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 23386, \"to\": 23393}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 23397, \"to\": 23401}, {\"ngram\": \"my adult dream\", \"from\": 23441, \"to\": 23455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since I have genuine love for both of these, I am willing to sacrifice the other things like not really having vacation time since I have to be full-time at the hospital, or not being able to hang out with my friends too much since I have to be at the field and go to the hospital after.\", \"from\": 23458, \"to\": 23745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genuine love\", \"from\": 23471, \"to\": 23483}, {\"ngram\": \"the other things\", \"from\": 23529, \"to\": 23545}, {\"ngram\": \"vacation time\", \"from\": 23569, \"to\": 23582}, {\"ngram\": \"full-time\", \"from\": 23602, \"to\": 23611}, {\"ngram\": \"the hospital\", \"from\": 23615, \"to\": 23627}, {\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 23664, \"to\": 23674}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 23706, \"to\": 23715}, {\"ngram\": \"the hospital\", \"from\": 23726, \"to\": 23738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's all worth it just because I have genuine love and care for doing both of the things that I am doing.\", \"from\": 23746, \"to\": 23859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genuine love\", \"from\": 23792, \"to\": 23804}, {\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 23832, \"to\": 23842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSTON, TEXAS - JUNE 03: Michelle Alozie #22 of the Houston Dash celebrates her goal with Diana Ordonez #11 and Maria Sanchez #7 during the first half against the Orlando Pride at Shell Energy Stadium on June 03, 2023 in Houston, Texas.\", \"from\": 23861, \"to\": 24098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23861, \"end\": 23875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9951469799537439, \"rank\": 0.00485244371065938, \"text\": \"HOUSTON, TEXAS\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 23887, \"end\": 23895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"score\": 0.8964401403798796, \"rank\": 0.11043514734633086, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\"}, {\"begin\": 23914, \"end\": 23926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Houston Dash\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Dash\"}, {\"begin\": 23952, \"end\": 23957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wonder_Woman\", \"score\": 0.9998801385760012, \"rank\": 0.00011987522491029696, \"text\