"college\", \"from\": 24461, \"to\": 24468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Connecticut like five years ago, I think it cost around $150 to get your hair braided.\", \"from\": 24514, \"to\": 24603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24517, \"end\": 24528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut\", \"score\": 0.9959554867153392, \"rank\": 0.0030030462363885443, \"text\": \"Connecticut\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your hair\", \"from\": 24585, \"to\": 24594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a broke college student, I could not even fathom giving someone that much money to braid my hair.\", \"from\": 24604, \"to\": 24704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a broke college student\", \"from\": 24607, \"to\": 24630}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 24663, \"to\": 24670}, {\"ngram\": \"that much money\", \"from\": 24671, \"to\": 24686}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 24696, \"to\": 24703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would just go on \\\"YouTube University\\\", and slowly braid the back of my hair and try things out over and over again.\", \"from\": 24705, \"to\": 24822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"YouTube University\", \"from\": 24725, \"to\": 24743}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 24763, \"to\": 24771}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 24775, \"to\": 24782}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 24791, \"to\": 24797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After so many years of trial and error, I am just so comfortable with braiding my hair.\", \"from\": 24823, \"to\": 24910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many years\", \"from\": 24829, \"to\": 24842}, {\"ngram\": \"trial\", \"from\": 24846, \"to\": 24851}, {\"ngram\": \"error\", \"from\": 24856, \"to\": 24861}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 24902, \"to\": 24909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I save so much money!\", \"from\": 24911, \"to\": 2493